      "id": "PopularPost188135",
      "post_content": "Protection is always good, but auras are notorious for causing card disadvantage. Although protection from {G}{U} is nice, the colours that have the most creature hate are {R} and {B}. As pointed out [Flickering Ward](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flickering Ward) is an interesting alternative, it is more effective against decks without {G}/{U} in them, but can provide less protection in some circumstances. Also [Flickering Ward](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flickering Ward) has the ability to return itself to your hand, thus negating the potential card disadvantage that could result.",
      "posted_by": "tcollins",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost188135\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Protection is always good, but auras are notorious for causing card disadvantage. Although protection from {G}{U} is nice, the colours that have the most creature hate are {R} and {B}. As pointed out <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flickering Ward\">Flickering Ward</a> is an interesting alternative, it is more effective against decks without {G}/{U} in them, but can provide less protection in some circumstances. Also <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flickering Ward\">Flickering Ward</a> has the ability to return itself to your hand, thus negating the potential card disadvantage that could result.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy44184\">tcollins</span>\r\n                                (8/15/2011 12:23:00 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_p